{"tid":1092784,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"艾美利暗示續約韋碧克","createTime":"2019-04-05T06:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T10:18:03.000Z","uid":19552,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"12cbc5820acedf7e272042896dbd77a15558de96","tid":1092784,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T06:25:30.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJ8yZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=ce8384f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】雖然前鋒韋碧克近季傷多過踢，但阿仙奴領隊艾美利仍然考慮季後跟他續約。<br />\n<br />\n28歲的韋碧克（Danny Welbeck）向來是「傷患磁石」，去年11月在歐霸盃右邊足踝受重創，今季很大機會未能復出。他跟阿仙奴的合約，在今季後就完結，令人擔心其球會前途。<br />\n<br />\n不過，艾美利對這名曼聯青訓產品投下信心一票：「他的康復進度很好，而且開始觸球訓練。今季，他很難回歸戰場了，但進度很好，或許軍醫會讓他在最後數周復操。之後，有關續約的事宜，他就要跟球會商討了。」<br />\n<br />\n艾美利暗示跟韋碧克續新約，或多或少因為他屬於英格蘭球員，事關兵工廠陣中的土炮不多，除了後衛洛賀丁、贊堅臣，就只有小將：「每支英格蘭球隊都需要英兵。韋碧克現時有傷在身，但他曾經入選代表隊。」"},{"pid":"5bc979a72b59be78301638f3e497d4eb031949b0","tid":1092784,"uid":30022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T06:28:35.000Z","msg":"跟我一齊shout"},{"pid":"295d1be7c5a307d1b8ca7cf50c2d0c7a2e092703","tid":1092784,"uid":20143,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T06:28:41.000Z","msg":"要靠佢吸哂d傷"},{"pid":"cc5fecafe102c95f3cac1653890ef41d28539d64","tid":1092784,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T06:44:07.000Z","msg":"雲加想開心"},{"pid":"7f411362a610d3da53f7cb1a9208cc11ece546b6","tid":1092784,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T06:53:42.000Z","msg":"文員頂比亞迪個位"},{"pid":"1ee7068f6ae9d70024117061679d0ca82e9bd8f9","tid":1092784,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T06:58:00.000Z","msg":"回家啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae18461dcbf313086e04f73d9ad36ff8838a1a71","tid":1092784,"uid":235174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T